posture. Shoulder straps are adjustable with 3 rows of hooks in the front to adjust to your
comfort.
* Our Reshaping Solution When Worn:

Adjustable straps helps to correct posture

Supports and flattens the abdomen

Can reduce up to 2 sizes

Helps straighten your torso
61% Polyamide, 33% Cotton, 6% Elastane

Special sizes by request
AVAILABLE COLORS: Black, Beige and White
